SEO Analyzer: Optimize Your Website Instantly
Effortlessly analyze and optimize your website's SEO with the SEO Analyzer Chrome Extension. This powerful tool provides detailed insights into your site's structure, including page titles, meta descriptions, headings, internal and external links, HTTP response headers, and server details—all at your fingertips.

Key Features:
✅ Quickly identify SEO issues for improved rankings.
✅ View and count internal and external links with precision.
✅ Analyze heading structures (H1 to H6) for better content hierarchy.
✅ Inspect HTTP response headers and server details for performance insights.
✅ Lightweight, fast, and user-friendly interface.

Whether you're a digital marketer, web developer, or website owner, SEO Analyzer is the ultimate companion for boosting your search engine performance. Install now to optimize your site like a pro!
